1
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:08,952
OWAI: Ladies and gentlemen, welcome aboard. We'll be landing in about an hour.

2
00:00:08,952 --> 00:00:10,536
TOM: This is taking forever.

3
00:00:10,536 --> 00:00:11,736
JERRY: I'm starving.

4
00:00:11,736 --> 00:00:16,752
AREEBA: Would you like a snack, sir? We have peanuts or pretzels.

5
00:00:16,752 --> 00:00:22,584
OWAI: Remember, please fasten your seatbelts. We'll be hitting some turbulence.

6
00:00:22,584 --> 00:00:29,505
OWAI: Don't worry, folks. We're going through a bit of turbulence. Just keep your seats and-

7
00:00:29,505 --> 00:00:31,448
JERRY: Ahh! This is crazy!

8
00:00:31,448 --> 00:00:33,823
TOM: Stay calm, Jerry. We'll be fine.

9
00:00:33,823 --> 00:00:38,313
AREEBA: Can I get you a blanket, sir? Or a cup of water?

10
00:00:38,313 --> 00:00:42,667
OWAI: How's it looking, Areeba? Any signs of trouble?

11
00:00:42,667 --> 00:00:49,267
AREEBA: No, Captain. Everything's looking good. Just a bit of turbulence.
